<!-- Container (The Band Section) -->
<div id="band" class="container text-center">
  <h3>THE FLYING DEZIRE BAND</h3>
  <p><em>We love music!</em></p>
  <p>We are Flying Dezire, an experimental rockband from the Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India with a 100% self-written repertoire. Our line up is: drums, bass guitar, singer, two guitarist and one keyboardist.

Throughout the years all of us have done different things / styles of music in different bands but none of us ever had the privilege to create and play the music which we wanted to. We always wanted to know how it would be but the situation never came.

we all have almost same kind of taste of music which brings our idea as well as our music to the next level. We all are very passionate about music and having deep enthausiasm. Also to be honest: We all met at the clash of bands playing from different band and after having friendly conversation we decided to work together and do things which we want to do.

and after that we jam together and soon...we started playing in many gig where we had huge crowd support, In our first gig we played about 15-20 minutes which will create some atmosphere in that concert (200-300 persons).

It would be really cool to meet someone who would want to help us out with this so we take guidence from many local bands and develop our skills. To make it easier (or maybe harder) we do not have a clear idea about how to create it or even what it should sound like. The idea in general is that it could start with strings (low / soft Dminor) with piano licks in Dminor + dissonants / raised 7th, going to a climax as where some massive drums will take over and the intro dies out.

We are releasing our debut album soon, stay tuned for more updates.</p>
  <br>
